{"tid":287540,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去過一次旅行 就知香港客一定係最閪","createTime":"2017-06-17T13:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T03:45:59.000Z","uid":38131,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86ea8696d7d77dd354d79f08afe9ae8cb0231e94","tid":287540,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"真係怕撚左班垃圾<br />\n岩岩去食迴轉壽司<br />\n兩條死肥閪毒撚由拎位<br />\n一路柒到出門口<br />\n諗唔明點樣食壽司可以食到人地條迴轉帶卡住左<br />\n仲要d碟炒埋一堆 野食都差d跌埋落黎<br />\n成條帶俾你整停左差唔多十分鐘<br />\n搞到幾個店員行埋黎服侍你兩條垃圾<br />\n知唔知醜嫁<br />\n<br />\n以後都唔敢同人地講係香港人<br />\n真係好撚肉酸<br />\n學好當地語言扮係本地人好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 自己一個好安靜<br />\n<br />\nBtw 個女店員都幾得意 對住佢笑佢又對番我笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6601bab833d4103b886524a5e7638060f39d0cd7","tid":287540,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:19:23.000Z","msg":"大家都係香港客，咁不如樓主講講自已有幾閪先啦，你唔係諗住去到外地扮當地人閪鳩香港人下話？"},{"pid":"90c474e373c1cfc695a8201b8a7a84d17d7976fa","tid":287540,"uid":38131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家都係香港客，咁不如樓主講講自已有幾閪先啦，你唔係諗住去到外地扮當地人閪鳩香港人下話？</blockquote><br />\n首先 我自己一個獨遊 安份守己<br />\n最低限度都尊重自己先<br />\n唔會大大聲講到全街都知你係外國人<br />\n然後 起碼唔會當眾出醜<br />\n我自己就唔識日文既<br />\n但有問題要問既時候<br />\n最少都嘗試同佢地講最基本既日文再加身體語言<br />\n再唔得就講句唔好意思再拎部電話出黎翻譯<br />\n無論解唔解決到都講句唔好意思阻住人地<br />\n最基本禮貌啦下嘛<br />\n你係香港都睇唔起班支那種大大聲唔該都冇聲問你野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74aab1fd42f17c4c3e9d6c45fc78d30e77fe801f","tid":287540,"uid":14348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"有朋友的毒撚同冇朋友的毒撚嘅分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b0498bb8d8a2423b8e1c65ccb5b40638e4fd98","tid":287540,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有朋友的毒撚同冇朋友的毒撚嘅分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實知唔知醜同人數冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知醜既應該知咩係基本禮儀<br />\n唔係叫你服侍班當地人<br />\n唔好阻撚住哂<br />\n柒下柒下咁就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ba3d9a21fc48297cf3ce8c928c4c63645ab52e","tid":287540,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"FEEL到樓主好毒sosad"},{"pid":"3ff5fce97e04a0cbf0dfb458286261d92da9f77d","tid":287540,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>FEEL到樓主好毒sosad</blockquote><br />\n自問又真係唔毒wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能我成日對住人微笑<br />\n人地都對番我笑掛<br />\n最起碼大家都開心<br />\n冇果種柒味先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60513ef7377f19089b8eb6e6893ed22e221369b","tid":287540,"uid":113546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>FEEL到樓主好毒sosad</blockquote><br />\n樓主毒咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個post既重點係講緊班人無禮儀<br />\n行為影響到其他人<br />\n我覺得喱啲人仲柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使樓主係毒<br />\n但佢都係條值得尊重 有禮貌既毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f337cdc8cddcf8c73d88fbd82346fe53e97249","tid":287540,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:19:14.000Z","msg":"你緊係靜啦<br />\n都無人同你講野唔通自問自答咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3db6d83ff5c16b34c5a4ea041b01b72280d7db","tid":287540,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:22:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你緊係靜啦<br />\n都無人同你講野唔通自問自答咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會唔會搞到人地成個場停哂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc04b942436145802249f3350963a9a9a677fc9","tid":287540,"uid":2373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"使乜去旅行，做過服務行業都知最閪一定係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0319d907a8cbb71dda5cc03d1ad2efe2903e88","tid":287540,"uid":38131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:26:07.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人覺得獨遊就係毒撚冇人陪<br />\n我行程頭5日行足四日山<br />\n每朝6點起身 行10個鐘<br />\n你敢唔敢跟足我行程呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n享受下獨遊唔洗處處就人地plan唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd2c0ab5197894ac419ff545aacf7620aa08827","tid":287540,"uid":96146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:27:02.000Z","msg":"唔洗去旅行都知香港客有幾閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過係外地 9成香港人同大陸人其實一鳩樣 <br />\n大大聲講野 冇禮貌 唔識尊重當地文化 <br />\n但大陸人多數都好肯洗錢 要臉<br />\n而香港人有部分人係樣樣計到盡 務求要平要抵 為左慳錢 再核突既行為都做得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3fa8f17aa02dbdc6a53c04e464f988aba3f2af","tid":287540,"uid":2195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:28:18.000Z","msg":"一向都講緊"},{"pid":"d35d62431ec14026f2ca5992f10975ec90b01d26","tid":287540,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一向都講緊</blockquote><br />\n本身都唔太覺得特別<br />\n但自從上飛機有條臭閪勁大聲屌鳩個空姐開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27365f5790922a60520a8a38f392b13553499a7e","tid":287540,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"搭程飛機都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗鬼去到當地"},{"pid":"60121d46b58c4e84f5b8670a86686e48af6e167e","tid":287540,"uid":13616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:41:40.000Z","msg":"好想知可以點樣整停條帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3956d9fef8e6c95f91e05c5cc49e6f4d89a316","tid":287540,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想知可以點樣整停條帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<br />\n隔離個日本仔話條帶停左<br />\n我再望一望果兩條肥仔<br />\n就見到幾兜炒埋左<br />\n跟住我見到佢地伸隻手入去拎番d唔知咩出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920e7dc207eb11d94f789103c5c5852b937c3364","tid":287540,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"唔洗去旅行, 做過下服務業已經知"},{"pid":"a6276ef851a3ec7a495b616004d304b7bb43a261","tid":287540,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去旅行 遇到嘅香港人 一係嘈 一係冇禮貌"}]}